{"id":161709,"type":4,"name":"ARK: Survival Evolved","name_cn":"方舟：生存进化","date":"2017-08-29","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8d/46/161709_KdM66.jpg","rating":{"rank":4177,"total":98,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":1,"4":3,"5":9,"6":24,"7":30,"8":22,"9":5,"10":3},"score":6.8},"summary":"《方舟：生存进化》（英语：Ark: Survival Evolved）是一款由Studio Wildcard制作与发行的生存类沙盒动作冒险游戏，使用虚幻4引擎打造，计划于2016年6月在Linux，Microsoft Windows，OS X，PlayStation 4和Xbox One平台发布。游戏的抢先体验版已于2015年6月2日登录Windows平台，7月1日登录Linux和OS X平台，12月16日登录Xbox One平台。游戏舞台设定在一座充满恐龙的神秘岛屿“方舟”，玩家必须运用技巧与智慧在危机四伏的世界中生存。\r\n\r\n游戏以第一人称或第三人称视角进行。在游戏世界中，玩家可以步行或者骑恐龙，可以使用枪械或简易武器来对抗敌对人类和生物，建立基地用以防御。玩家也可以利用从游戏中搜刮的资源打造自己的武器。游戏可以选择单人游戏或多人游戏，其中多人游戏可以允许多名玩家同时在线参与。\r\n\r\n游戏于2014年10月开始制作，开发团队为了在游戏玩法上有所创新，对恐龙的外貌进行了大量研究。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>方舟：生存进化</li><li><span>平台: </span>Nintendo Switch</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox One</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS4</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ARPG</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Unreal Engine 4</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>多人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2017年8月29日</li><li><span>售价: </span>$39,9</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.playark.com/</li>","collection":{"on_hold":30,"dropped":18,"wish":48,"collect":128,"doing":14},"tags":[{"name":"生存","count":19},{"name":"STEAM","count":14},{"name":"PC","count":12},{"name":"ARPG","count":6},{"name":"XboxOne","count":4},{"name":"2017","count":4},{"name":"Android","count":3},{"name":"PS4","count":3},{"name":"开放世界","count":2},{"name":"SIM","count":1},{"name":"大作游戏","count":1},{"name":"XGP","count":1},{"name":"合作","count":1},{"name":"XONE","count":1},{"name":"☆","count":1},{"name":"AAVG","count":1},{"name":"网游","count":1},{"name":"EPIC","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"relations":[{"id":387236,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/81/3c/387236_6N8VE.jpg","title":"ARK 2","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/387236"},{"id":242025,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/co